data.description: Spacious house at a great price in St. James Place, a small community bordering Royal Pines CC. Located in Coosa School District, just minutes from downtown, military bases & the beach. The home offers a wide-open floor plan w/a separate formal DR/office, a ground floor MBR, a screen room & 4 additional BRs upstairs & one very spacious room w/a 1/2 bath & an open playroom/2nd living room at top of stairs.  Hardwood floors, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances & a gas fireplace. The backyard is fully fenced, large pool & deck. One side of the property borders a vacant wooded lot & there's no potential development across the street.
